data.description: Beautiful views from every corner of this 3 bedroom, 3bath, 2028-SF, quality built & well maintained home on a .97 acre lot. Large open concept w/cathedral ceilings. Kitchen has a walk-in pantry and bay window & eating area. Spacious MBR suite w/walk-in closet, jetted tub and it's own covered patio & exterior access. 20x40 heated garage/shop w/ 14' door which includes a full gym area and upper storage. Private Well & Septic, Kinetico water softener, Finished man-cave/gathering room  features a efficiency kitchen, Office/Den with full bathroom. There are multiple cover patio's located @ front and rear of home. Nicely landscaped and fully fenced yard and access Driveway gate.  Home also has a full security system w/monthly monitoring your home while away
